Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你还是离我而去时的那副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============op===============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.43,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:55.63,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:11.28,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:21.75,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:33.83,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:44.42,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:50.58,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:56.43,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:02:00.80,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.14,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:07.15,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.43,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:55.63,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们在倒错的精神世界中相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.87,0:01:11.28,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我们眼里的世界总是相互颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:21.75,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,这几乎要被认定为是无可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:33.83,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口淌泪的眼眸 在内心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:44.42,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的两人来不及结合便听到离别的倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:50.58,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:56.43,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们像渐趋衰老的动物一样相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:02:00.80,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,你美得令人落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:04.14,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,在倒错的精神世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:07.15,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我想细细体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============op===============
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MI·XY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.67,0:02:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽西亚室有入侵者 艾丽西亚室有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标就一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封锁通道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云大人 请退后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要退下的是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在接到新的命令之前先在外面待命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有翅膀的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到这么快就和你重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被夏娃施加到Altair的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娃的诅咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样暂时就不会有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喉咙还有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道阿马塔同学他们是否平安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他答应过我不会乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答应…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与之交换 希望能你也能答应我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从地面上几乎看不到天空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能因为这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家才憧憬着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才对“Aquaria舞动于空”如此着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin也曾是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才好险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这里也不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特到底在哪里溜达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 那个游手好闲的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总算掌握了支配这个世界的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但话说回来 这些顶盖真是大煞风景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是削弱生命的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这片大地跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在等候即将来临的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此我可以感受得到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所展现的力量的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及力量所汇聚的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把我关在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要进到里面来 一切都好办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为找出不动总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来到了这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人十分引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而很容易就能找到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能为帮到大家的就只有这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这次不会再逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会找到总司令并带他回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 修修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总算发现我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.63,0:07:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么总算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是拼命地四处找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要找我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是市场里 还是在有轨电车里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又或是在这个港口城市里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:08:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都一动不动地站在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体置于相互交错的万物中也决不动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的灵魂置于川流不息的时间中也决不挪移
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不挪移…不动摇…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.69,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不为万物所动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名为不动·ZEN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不动总司令从一万二千年前开始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确来说是从二万四千年前开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃·铃白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想弄清一切真相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定不会逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕真相有多么残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要的就是这股气魄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候是残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距今12年前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的Igler…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是女性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从Altair这颗星球上绝迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jin·无双是最后一个在Altair诞生的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.79,0:09:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Igler已经绝迹的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能等着慢慢走向灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们才会从我们的地球上掠走女性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是需要一个能孕育出Altair的未来的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.72,0:09:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太恣意妄为了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能听到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相还有后续
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且将更为残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix 你等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 给我乖乖就范
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是前几天被你们老大抓回来的大胸女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能开出比那黑亮的口子更大的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样放过你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的挖洞能力对生物根本不奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.54,0:11:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俘虏跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会找到你 然后将你拥入怀里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御子乃·铃白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这个甜甜圈如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得如何…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜甜圈在我手中静止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际上却以相同于船的速度在海上移动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡海的甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得很不可思议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说穿了就是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事物有时因为过于接近反而看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在应该在总司令腹中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否当真如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,构成甜甜圈的微粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纵使遭到分解也不会消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被摄入我体内之后可谓处于永远静止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从刚才开始就一味在进行着类似修禅问答的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有真相到底是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.04,0:12:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跨越一万二千年的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续支撑着这星球大地的永恒的不动尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恒的不动尊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的神话型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就沉睡在这趟旅程的终点之上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找不到丝毫的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在X33区
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去捉住他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云大人独自留在艾丽西亚室里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自Vega的侵略者也在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娃的诅咒不仅让我们星球上的Igler全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连从你们的世界带来的众多Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也同样遭到了诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们好不容易终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能抵御Altair的诅咒的稀有Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rare·Igler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连最强的Rare·Igler艾丽西亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也很遗憾地没能胜任真正的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们凭什么权利把妈妈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是为了维系Altair的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒是什么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你们从地球上捉来的女性现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷达以及红外线传感器皆无反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独重力波传感器有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离是?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离90
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,80
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,60
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,40
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离0
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婕希卡 柚叶 你们还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而使用过力量的柚叶更令人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.83,0:15:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.50,0:15:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是混账
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们两人的身体到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到吗 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在你脚下的塔内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你归还的排场还真大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不是一起的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像到了一个叫艾丽西亚室的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是被施加到Altair的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一开始也无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要亲眼目睹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都只能够接受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…SPADA的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是机械天使吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔 快坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作要快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去婕希卡和柚叶的身体会支持不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事我非说不可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出云大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您退后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那里 开火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也唤来了预备的Vector
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们坐到那上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶和婕希卡在上空待机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就拜托了 伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柚叶 你那措辞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管那个了 专心对敌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,                    concerto
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有了女性那优美的 协奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.84,0:17:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法演奏禁断的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调音合体 Go Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我们时间不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,                           Toccata
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我匆匆弹上一首最为轻快的 托卡塔曲 吧
